WEBVTT

00:00.548 --> 00:03.774
<i>Nine years ago I witnessed</i>
<i>my mother's murder.</i>

00:03.775 --> 00:06.694
<i>I would have been killed, too,</i>
<i>if it hadn't been for Vincent.</i>

00:06.696 --> 00:09.647
<i>I was part of an experimental</i>
<i>special forces group.</i>

00:09.649 --> 00:11.682
<i>Their goal was to create</i>
<i>the perfect super soldier.</i>

00:11.684 --> 00:13.150
<i>But something went wrong.</i>

00:13.152 --> 00:14.702
You're him.

00:14.704 --> 00:15.870
The most
eligible bachelor

00:15.872 --> 00:18.005
has reverted to online dating?
Claire Sinclair?

00:18.007 --> 00:19.507
<i>Evan's getting closer</i>
<i>and closer.</i>

00:19.509 --> 00:22.460
It's him.
It's our creature.

00:22.462 --> 00:24.629
I managed to disrupt
one of his studies.

00:24.631 --> 00:26.781
- Vincent Keller.
<i>- Who is she?</i>

00:26.783 --> 00:28.466
<i>We were pretty close.</i>

00:28.468 --> 00:30.518
<i>Why didn't you tell me</i>
<i>you were engaged?</i>

00:30.520 --> 00:32.853
Alex is willing to give up
her life

00:32.855 --> 00:34.055
to go with me.

00:34.057 --> 00:36.357
<i>My enemies are still out there.</i>

00:36.359 --> 00:37.808
<i>And they want me dead.</i>

00:39.394 --> 00:41.195
You ripped those men apart.

00:41.197 --> 00:42.446
I would never hurt you.

00:42.448 --> 00:43.531
I can't.

00:43.533 --> 00:44.966
We can't.

00:44.968 --> 00:46.517
It was never about

00:46.519 --> 00:48.185
taking off with Alex.

00:48.187 --> 00:50.504
It was about a better future
for me.

00:50.506 --> 00:52.740
Vincent,
I can't be your second choice.

